 <span data-ttu-id="4bc54-106">L’implémentation de <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bc54-106">The implementation of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TtsEngineSsml.Speak%2A></span></span>  
  
1.  <span data-ttu-id="4bc54-107">Reçoit un tableau de <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances et crée un tableau de <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances doit être passé à la `Speak` méthode sur un moteur de synthèse sous-jacent.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4bc54-107">Receives an array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances and creates a new array of <xref:System.Speech.Synthesis.TtsEngine.TextFragment> instances to be passed to the `Speak` method on an underlying synthesis engine.</span></span>  
  
